      <p>The app provides you with:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>- Early access to new releases</li>
        <li>- App exclusive product launches</li>
        <li>- App exclusive discounts</li>
        <li>- Smoother shopping experience</li>
        <li>- Up to date alerts and notifications</li>
        <li>- Checkout with Apple Pay</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  
  <div class="download-sec">
    <h1>Download The App</h1>
    <div class="btn-holder">
      <div class="btn-sec btn-app-store">
        <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/the-couture-club/id1482034648" target="_blank"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0242/6047/6980/files/APPLE-BADGE.png?v=1654667831" alt="img" class="img-fluid"></a>
      </div>
      <div class="btn-sec btn-play-store">
        <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=co.tapcart.app.id_P35DnMmRpS&amp;hl=en_GB&amp;gl=US" target="_blank"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0242/6047/6980/files/GOOGLE-BADGE.png?v=1654667831" alt="img" class="img-fluid"></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


